    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut each <strong>plant-based sausage roll </strong>into 5, brush the tops of the pastry with a little <strong>cold water</strong> and sprinkle over your<strong> nigella seeds</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>in the oven for 20 min or until golden and cooked through and puffed up at the edges</p>",
