      "instruction": "<p>Chop your<strong> potatoes</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> to a pot with plenty of<strong> boiled water </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 15 min or until fork-tender, then drain and set aside to steam dry</p>",
