      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely dice your<strong> red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Dice your<strong> tomato[es]</strong></p><p>Heat a pot over a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and once hot, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
