    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your<strong> chives</strong> finely, then combine them with your <strong>Dijon mustard</strong>, <strong>remaining cider vinegar </strong>and 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil </strong>– this is your <strong>herby dressing</strong></p><p>Slice your<strong> apple[s] </strong>finely</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Gently mix the<strong> sliced apple </strong>and <strong>salad</strong> together with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>in a separate bowl<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>apple salad</strong></p>",
